"title": "6620: calling",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6620",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's summoning of individuals and people to himself, so that they will belong to him and serve him in his world. The calling of a believer may involve a specific place, task or vocation in life.</p>\n<h2>God calls individuals to belong to him and serve him</h2>\n<h3>God calls all people everywhere</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:30\">ACT 17:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:4\">PRO 8:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:22\">ISA 45:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:1\">ISA 55:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:13\">MAT 9:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:30\">MAT 11:28–11:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:9\">MAT 22:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:37\">JHN 7:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:39\">ACT 2:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:18\">ROM 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:4\">PSA 19:4</a></p>\n<h3>Few respond positively to God's call</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:14\">MAT 22:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:12\">ISA 65:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:4\">ISA 66:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:13\">JER 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:17\">JER 35:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:2-Matt22:10\">MAT 22:2–22:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:16-Luke14:24\">LUK 14:16–14:24</a></p>\n<h3>Responding to God's call results in salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:15\">HEB 9:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:1\">JUD 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:25\">JHN 5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:3\">JHN 10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:6\">ROM 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28-Rom8:30\">ROM 8:28–8:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:29\">ROM 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:9\">1CO 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:24-1Cor1:29\">1CO 1:24–1:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:18-1Cor7:22\">1CO 7:18–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:6\">GAL 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1\">EPH 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:14\">PHP 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:11\">2TH 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:14\">2TH 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:12\">1TI 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:1\">HEB 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:3\">2PE 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:10\">2PE 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:14\">REV 17:14</a></p>\n<h2>God calls Christians to live differently</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9\">2TI 1:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:15\">1CO 7:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15\">COL 3:15</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:13\">GAL 5:13</a> <em>serving one another</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18\">EPH 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:4\">EPH 4:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:20-1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:20–2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:9\">1PE 3:9</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:7\">1TH 4:7</a></p>\n<h2>God called particular individuals to do specific tasks at specific times</h2>\n<p>Abraham:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:3\">GEN 12:1–12:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:2\">ISA 51:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:8\">HEB 11:8</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:4\">EXO 3:4</a> <em>Moses</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:4-1Sam3:10\">1SA 3:4–3:10</a> <em>Samuel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:8\">ISA 6:8</a> <em>Isaiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:2\">ISA 41:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:4\">ISA 45:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:6\">ISA 42:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:1\">ISA 49:1</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:4-Jer1:5\">JER 1:4–1:5</a> <em>Jeremiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos1:2\">HOS 1:2</a> <em>Hosea</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:15\">AMO 7:15</a> <em>Amos</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:1-Jonah1:2\">JON 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:1-Jonah3:2\">JON 3:1–3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:18-Matt4:22\">MAT 4:18–4:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:16-Mark1:20\">MRK 1:16–1:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:2-Luke5:11\">LUK 5:2–5:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:35-John1:42\">JHN 1:35–1:42</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">ACT 13:2</a> <em>Barnabas and Paul</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:1\">ROM 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:1\">1CO 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:15\">GAL 1:15</a></p>\n<h2>God called a people, Israel, to serve him in a special way</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:1\">ISA 43:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1-Hos11:2\">HOS 11:1–11:2</a></p>\n<h2>The believer's place in life is understood to be a calling</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:17\">1CO 7:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:20\">1CO 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:24\">1CO 7:24</a></p>",
